---
// Philosophy section - "What We Believe"
---

<section id="philosophy" class="relative py-32 md:py-48 z-10">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 md:gap-24 items-center">
      <!-- Visual (Fibonacci Spiral) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5 relative group">
        <div class="aspect-[1/1.2] glass-panel rounded-sm relative overflow-hidden">
          <!-- Overlay Vector -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center p-12">
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 100 100"
              class="w-full h-full text-white/20 group-hover:text-lituus-pink/40 transition-colors duration-700"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <circle
                cx="50"
                cy="50"
                r="48"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="0.5"
              ></circle>
              <circle
                cx="50"
                cy="50"
                r="30"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="0.5"
              ></circle>
              <path
                d="M50 50 L50 2 A48 48 0 0 1 98 50"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="0.5"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6">
            <div class="w-full h-px bg-white/10 mb-2"></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-end">
              <span class="font-serif italic text-2xl text-white">
                Fig. 1
              </span>
              <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-lituus-pink">
                The Augur's Staff
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5 lg:col-span-7 space-y-10">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-lituus-pink/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-lituus-pink"></span>
          <span class="text-[10px] font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-[#e8c5d1]">
            What We Believe
          </span>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-light text-white leading-tight">
          Truth without
          <span class="font-serif italic text-lituus-pink ml-2">
            Permission
          </span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-xl font-light text-slate-300 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
          Truth shouldn't require permission or gatekeepers. Like the ancient
          augurs who interpreted divine will through natural observation, we
          believe technology can reveal truth through mathematical certainty
          and economic incentivesâ€”not human authority.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-12 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-14 aspect-square text-4xl font-serif text-lituus-pink p-2 mb-2 border border-white/20">
              &phi;
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-white mb-2">
              Transparency
            </h4>
            <p class="text-sm font-light">
              Decentralized systems prove themselves worthy through aligned
              incentives.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-14 aspect-square text-4xl font-serif text-lituus-pink p-2 mb-2 border border-white/20">
              &infin;
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-white mb-2">
              Rationality
            </h4>
            <p class="text-sm font-light">
              Honesty emerges naturally because it is always the most rational
              choice.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
